WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.360
Shah Rukh Khan: In today’s day
of information

00:00:05.360 --> 00:00:07.280
there is still, at places, a lack of data.

00:00:07.280 --> 00:00:11.040
And at others, there is a need to understand
how this data can be used.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.920
Prukalpa Sankar and her team
are bridging this gap

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:16.020
and ensuring through their data company


00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:18.400
that the right information reaches
the right person

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:22.080
so that all of us have a chance
to see a better tomorrow.

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:23.840
TED Talks India welcomes

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:27.520
Delhi-based young innovator
Prukalpa Sankar.

00:00:28.060 --> 00:00:29.530
Prukalpa Sankar.

00:00:29.570 --> 00:00:32.570
(Applause)